-Laundromat.
-Come again?

14:29.125 --> 14:31.834
-Laundromat.
-A laundromat?

14:32.166 --> 14:34.500
-Uh-huh.
-Really?

14:35.000 --> 14:36.291
Yeah, you know,
you see, Dawson,

14:36.291 --> 14:38.041
in a small town
such as Capeside,

14:38.500 --> 14:40.375
everybody, except for those

14:40.375 --> 14:43.375
with questionable hygiene
sensibilities, of course,

14:43.917 --> 14:46.083
has to do their laundry
at some point.

14:46.625 --> 14:48.291
So, you're saying

14:48.291 --> 14:49.750
you would stake out
the laundromat.

14:51.041 --> 14:52.083
Exactly.

14:53.000 --> 14:54.917
♪ [MUSIC] ♪

14:55.792 --> 14:56.834
