all about Eve?

15:20.417 --> 15:21.375
Yeah.

15:21.375 --> 15:22.000
[LAUGHS]

15:22.375 --> 15:23.750
Let me give you
a little life lesson

15:23.750 --> 15:25.959
-from the Witter vault, Dawson.
-Oh, God.

15:27.250 --> 15:29.500
There are some women
who will come

15:29.500 --> 15:31.083
onto the movie set
that is your life,

15:31.083 --> 15:33.083
and function solely
as day players.

15:33.458 --> 15:35.917
They'll show up, they'll know
their dialogue,

15:35.917 --> 15:37.083
they'll hit their marks,

15:37.083 --> 15:38.959
they'll occasionally
steal a scene or 2 from you,

15:38.959 --> 15:40.583
but they will remain
always and forever

15:40.583 --> 15:42.000
an impenetrable mystery.

15:43.125 --> 15:45.333
But Eve barged into my life,

15:45.333 --> 15:47.917
