15:52.250 --> 15:54.083
where no girl has gone before?

15:54.458 --> 15:55.458
Synopsize with me.

15:56.000 --> 15:59.250
She works in a strip club,
but she doesn't, all right?

15:59.250 --> 16:00.625
She says she goes
to our school,

16:00.625 --> 16:01.625
but she doesn't.

16:01.625 --> 16:03.291
She appears, she disappears.

16:03.291 --> 16:05.166
She reappears without
rhyme or reason,

16:05.166 --> 16:06.208
who the hell is this girl?

16:06.208 --> 16:08.166
Whoa, ok, simmer down, Dawson.

16:09.166 --> 16:11.834
This girl is giving you
a meltdown, God.

16:13.291 --> 16:14.375
All right,
here's what I propose.

16:14.625 --> 16:16.250
You and I take a little trip
down to the video store,

16:16.250 --> 16:17.959
you want uh,
film noir, right?

16:18.291 --> 16:19.792
How about that one
with Matt Dillon

16:19.792 --> 16:22.417
where he has that really
outstanding threesome

16:22.417 --> 16:23.583
with Neve Campbell
and that chick

16:23.583 --> 16:25.000
from Starship Troopers?

16:29.291 --> 16:31.125
Yeah. Oh, hey,
one more thing.

16:31.125 --> 16:33.959
My brother. He, uh,
he gave you

16:33.959 --> 16:35.458
the laundromat speech,
didn't he?

16:35.458 --> 16:36.542
Yeah.

16:36.542 --> 16:38.166
[LAUGHS]

16:39.542 --> 16:42.708
♪ [NOIR SAXOPHONE MUSIC] ♪

16:43.834 --> 16:45.583
