17:00.333 --> 17:03.000
but it's a tad too
Andy of Mayberry for my taste.

17:03.542 --> 17:07.250
Given my druthers, I much prefer
Sheriff Dad's dissertation

17:07.250 --> 17:09.208
on how to pin a tail
on the suspect.

17:12.916 --> 17:14.416
Watch and learn, my friend.

17:22.208 --> 17:24.875
[BELL RINGS]

17:27.083 --> 17:29.583
Uh, miss? A little
service here, please?

17:29.875 --> 17:30.708
Very funny.

