17:48.125 --> 17:50.708
Wait till you see her, Potter,
She's a cutie.

17:51.291 --> 17:54.208
About your age, too.
A better dresser, though.

17:54.667 --> 17:57.458
Not so uptight
about showing off a little skin.

17:59.250 --> 18:00.792
I'm gonna get
so lucky tonight.

18:00.792 --> 18:03.083
Don't tell me you actually
found some high school girl

18:03.083 --> 18:04.458
so riddled
with insecurities

18:04.458 --> 18:06.500
