for your minor league

18:06.500 --> 18:08.375
Humbert Humbert
impersonations?

18:15.250 --> 18:16.542
Hey, Joey.

18:17.750 --> 18:19.500
Isn't this great?

18:19.500 --> 18:21.250
I was at the country club
today with my dad,

18:21.250 --> 18:22.417
'cause he's thinking
about joining,

18:22.417 --> 18:23.417
and I ran into Rob.

18:24.083 --> 18:25.917
I didn't know you
two knew each other.

18:25.917 --> 18:27.542
Oh, sure. He went
to prep school

18:27.542 --> 18:28.667
with my brother, Tim.

18:29.000 --> 18:31.834
So, did you know
that Joey and I were friends?

18:31.834 --> 18:33.750
Oh, I had a sneaking
suspicion.

18:34.417 --> 18:36.542
After all,
it is a small town.

18:37.875 --> 18:40.834
So, Andie, where's moneybags
taking you tonight?

18:41.333 --> 18:43.250
All the way down
to the Bahamas and back?

18:43.625 --> 18:45.625
No, you know,
we're just going to the movies.

18:45.625 --> 18:47.041
It's too hot to
do anything else.

18:47.375 --> 18:49.959
Well, almost anything else.

18:50.583 --> 18:53.500
That wasn't a sexual
overture, was it?

18:53.500 --> 18:56.375
Shh, Andie.
Not in front of the K-I-D.

18:58.834 --> 19:00.834
-I'm all finished here.
-Great.

19:03.458 --> 19:06.208
Here you go, Potter.
Buy yourself something pretty.

19:09.458 --> 19:11.000
Save it for bail money.

19:13.333 --> 19:16.708
Ok. Let's see
what this puppy can do.

19:19.750 --> 19:21.458
[ENGINE REVS]

19:21.458 --> 19:22.542
Bye, Joey!

19:33.542 --> 19:35.000
What a coincidence.

19:39.166 --> 19:40.417
Moonlight.

19:40.875 --> 19:42.291
Tell her how nice she looks.

19:42.792 --> 19:45.000
What a beautiful spot this is.

19:45.667 --> 19:49.500
Don't puke, don't puke,
don't puke, don't puke,
don't puke.

19:50.333 --> 19:52.500
-Henry?
-Uh...

19:52.500 --> 19:53.708
You ok?

19:53.708 --> 19:54.667
Uh...

19:55.166 --> 19:58.166
Uh, gulp once for yes,
twice for no.

19:58.750 --> 19:59.792
[GULPS ONCE]

19:59.792 --> 20:02.208
Once. Good, ok.

20:04.667 --> 20:06.083
What's on your hand?

20:06.083 --> 20:07.250
Uh, nothing.

20:07.834 --> 20:09.708
-Jen?
-Yeah?

20:10.166 --> 20:12.834
You, you're awesome.

20:13.625 --> 20:16.375
You look awesome,
you smell awesome,

20:16.375 --> 20:18.417
everything about you
is awesome.

20:19.583 --> 20:21.792
I, I just, I wanted you
to know that.

20:22.166 --> 20:23.333
[LAUGHS]

20:25.000 --> 20:29.041
Uh, good to know.
So, what are you doing here?

20:29.875 --> 20:32.250
Hanging...
Out, you know?

20:32.708 --> 20:35.166
The same thing you are,
just, just hanging out.

20:35.834 --> 20:37.542
Actually, I'm just
waiting for Jack.

20:37.875 --> 20:40.000
Oh, well, Jack
couldn't be here tonight,

20:40.000 --> 20:43.041
see, because he had these
other plans.

20:43.542 --> 20:46.667
Important plans, so, so he sent
me instead.

20:47.250 --> 20:49.667
Ok, I think I know
where this is going.

20:50.417 --> 20:51.291
Continue.

20:51.291 --> 20:53.834
Um, that's, that's it.

20:53.834 --> 20:55.208
Out with it, Henry.

20:56.125 --> 20:57.959
Well, I, I guess
he thought

20:57.959 --> 21:00.917
if you were here
and I were here,

21:00.917 --> 21:02.667
and we were both...

21:03.458 --> 21:04.542
-Here.
-Here.

21:04.542 --> 21:05.917
Together.

21:05.917 --> 21:07.500
Then it would sort of be
like a date,

21:07.500 --> 21:09.083
you know, like
our first date?

21:09.083 --> 21:10.542
Look, Henry, I know
that you're new at this

21:10.542 --> 21:13.208
being all of, uh,
I don't know, what, 14?

21:13.917 --> 21:14.917
15.

21:14.917 --> 21:16.250
Ok, 15.

21:16.708 --> 21:18.083
Dating is a consensual activity

21:18.083 --> 21:20.542
that usually involves
some sort of pre-arrangement.

21:21.166 --> 21:23.500
Next time, don't skip the part
where you ask me.

21:25.667 --> 21:28.250
-♪ [MUSIC] ♪
-[CRICKETS CHIRPING]

21:28.583 --> 21:30.542
[GRASS RUSTLING]

21:31.792 --> 21:33.000
[SIGHS]

21:38.834 --> 21:42.834
♪ [NOIR SAXOPHONE MUSIC] ♪

21:47.166 --> 21:51.125
